#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.13:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Anusayavagga"
msgstr "2. Tendencies"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 13. Kulasutta → kulūpagamanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Kulasutta"
msgstr "13. A Family"

# This a really odd sutta. You shouldn’t go to a family for alms just because they don’t give the best stuff? Seriously?
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.13:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgataṃ kulaṃ anupagantvā vā nālaṃ "
"upagantuṃ, upagantvā vā nālaṃ upanisīdituṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, visiting a family with seven factors is not worthwhile, or if "
"you’ve already arrived, sitting down is not worthwhile."

msgctxt "an7.13:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"Na manāpena paccuṭṭhenti, na manāpena abhivādenti, na manāpena āsanaṃ denti, "
"santamassa pariguhanti, bahukampi thokaṃ denti, paṇītampi lūkhaṃ denti, "
"asakkaccaṃ denti no sakkaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t politely rise, bow, or offer a seat. They hide what they have. "
"Even when they have much they give little. Even when they have refined "
"things they give coarse things. They give carelessly, not carefully."

msgctxt "an7.13:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi aṅgehi samannāgataṃ kulaṃ anupagantvā vā nālaṃ "
"upagantuṃ, upagantvā vā nālaṃ upanisīdituṃ."
msgstr ""
"Visiting a family with these seven factors is not worthwhile, or if you’ve "
"already arrived, sitting down is not worthwhile."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.13:2.1"
msgid ""
"Sattahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgataṃ kulaṃ anupagantvā vā alaṃ upagantuṃ, "
"upagantvā vā alaṃ upanisīdituṃ."
msgstr ""
"Visiting a family with seven factors is worthwhile, or if you’ve already "
"arrived, sitting down is worthwhile."

msgctxt "an7.13:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.13:2.3"
msgid ""
"Manāpena paccuṭṭhenti, manāpena abhivādenti, manāpena āsanaṃ denti, "
"santamassa na pariguhanti, bahukampi bahukaṃ denti, paṇītampi paṇītaṃ denti, "
"sakkaccaṃ denti no asakkaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They politely rise, bow, and offer a seat. They don’t hide what they have. "
"When they have much they give much. When they have refined things they give "
"refined things. They give carefully, not carelessly."

msgctxt "an7.13:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi aṅgehi samannāgataṃ kulaṃ anupagantvā vā alaṃ "
"upagantuṃ, upagantvā vā alaṃ upanisīditun”ti."
msgstr ""
"Visiting a family with these seven factors is worthwhile, or if you’ve "
"already arrived, sitting down is worthwhile.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.13:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
